description: Itubagus Token is an ERC20 Token that runs on Ethereum's Blockchain network. Supplay FIX 100 Million Tokens Only and less than 1% distributed in 2019. ITB Tokens are made to support and balance the price of Rizubot Tokens where 1 ITB Token is equivalent to 1000 RZB Tokens. In the future, 1% of total supplay will be burned from January 2020 to 2026, leaving only 16% of supplay.
